{"tid":1813754,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"報稅一問","createTime":"2020-01-06T13:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T14:12:30.000Z","uid":296536,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"098191e65768dcbeebf1f3644d7b489bd9672eab","tid":1813754,"uid":296536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T13:27:28.000Z","msg":"例子如下：<br />\n<br />\n父母夠55歲，阿爸有翻工交稅，阿媽冇翻工，阿爸寫左阿媽配偶免稅額。我係獨生子，有比家用佢地。<br />\n<br />\n問1：我可唔可以寫供養阿爸免稅額？<br />\n問2：我可唔可以寫供養阿媽免稅額？<br />\n<br />\n求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />主要唔確定係唔知寫唔寫得阿媽，因為阿爸已經寫左佢嘅配偶免稅額。"},{"pid":"73600a87630335c43c23bf14d749a494bf2c310b","tid":1813754,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T13:34:38.000Z","msg":"1. 家用唔係供養, no <br />\n2. 你老母幾多歲？但係你老豆 claim 咗都應該唔得<br />\n<br />\n求其他解答"},{"pid":"628bc7332840a72f9b2c746f6cfd770ee1f2c93a","tid":1813754,"uid":4057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T13:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c02b093b54a03cfc6c932010f6365cf8f9ccbb","tid":1813754,"uid":4057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"628bc7332840a72f9b2c746f6cfd770ee1f2c93a","tid":1813754,"uid":4057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T13:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T13:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27be2c98d9be7e428941fcce0da64d6c4f9bc0f9","tid":1813754,"uid":296536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:12:30.000Z","msg":"唔該哂巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}